The kitchen is fully equipped with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, a massive island and quiet close cabinets. The bathrooms are gorgeous and plenty large. Located in the Brentwood subdivision you are zoned for the highly desire Deep Creek school district. Come view this home today!
